name: ViewDisplaySettings

properties.description: Slower performance; displays high-resolution graphics and high-quality transparencies and turns on anti-aliasing.
properties.name: HIGH_QUALITY

properties.description: Moderate performance speed; displays proxy graphics and low-quality transparencies and turns on anti-aliasing.
properties.name: TYPICAL

properties.description: Best performance; grays out graphics and turns off transparency and anti-aliasing.
properties.name: OPTIMIZED

description: Options for display performance settings, which influence the speed and quality with which an object draws and redraws.
